Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where on earth are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:28.16,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いったいどこへ連れていくの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're about to see is the\Nbrain of this world as well as its heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.53,JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,「今からあなたが目にするのは
